response.original_title: Great American Scenic Railroads, Volume 5 of 6, Durango and Silverton & Cumbres and Toltec
response.overview: Durango and Silverton - Chasms and curves, crevasses, gorges and perilous passes. Take a thrill ride on one of the most spectacular train lines in the country. Cumbres and Toltec - Climb aboard Mikado Steam Locomotive No. 488 for a historic ride on the Cumbres & Toltec Scenic Railroad over the dramatic landscape of northern New Mexico and southern Colorado. Note: This is part five of a series of six parts.
response.title: Great American Scenic Railroads, Volume 5 of 6, Durango and Silverton & Cumbres and Toltec
